Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:40.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}她说着低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:47.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这一夜 我流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:55.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冰冷彻骨 仿如冻雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:03:01.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}洒落的现实 无处可避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:08.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:12.43,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅为这理由而束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Heart  My Story
