Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda的所在?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我可就爱莫能助了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者也有不知道的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假使我知道它在何处 你们又打算对Veda如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda原本就是为辅佐我们而设计制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就告诉我们 你们打算使用Veda做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧利亚构筑这项计划的真意何在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为即将到来的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到来的对话?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是人类的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不见得是万能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沦为阶下囚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我故意的 这样的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷特纳尔小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她射伤拉塞先生 还把米蕾娜抓作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷特纳尔小姐她自称 是变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽她?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.36,0:01:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果有什么情况 人质性命难保
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和艾纽作为同类型 思想能够相连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽 按计划行事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内的系统被…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷…雷特纳尔小姐 别这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还来得及…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想再往前走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么知道我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为只有你们能用脑量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}舰内系统被病毒感染?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成两组搜寻米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐请去舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 艾纽去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯小姐你来啦 有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 忘记了你的存在 C级别的脑量子使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有缺陷的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是一切的元凶 为上校报仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清英先生 史特拉特斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算抛弃我一个人走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意和我一起来? 能看到世界的变革喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Right 一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外附赠Cherudim一台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样了 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必真打 受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质被救走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要制作成女的 最后因为感情坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽用小艇脱离了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这系统是怎么回事 太不顺手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三闸门自动打开 后部闸门也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动Cherudim和00
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 一时疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借口跟利冯兹说去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 抱歉得优先夺回0-Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用TRANS-AM了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕伤到这台机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有优秀的战术预报员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser 合体模式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统控制权被00…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如洛克昂所说 远谈不上万能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已 只能对0-Raiser死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 留点纪念…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算过分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser的功率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要杀我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽·雷特纳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪啊 瞄准狙击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为何身在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何加入KATARON…加入天人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:09:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没出息了 莱尔·狄兰提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的觉悟就只有这种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔·狄兰提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的爱你 莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说身体欠佳 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你需要新的药方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔马克 我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供药物抑制你体内细胞异常造成的侵害 究竟是为了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你主动要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为实现没有纷争的统一世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为父母报仇 向Gundam讨还血债
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
